title: Address Merged Ports
tags:
  - freebsd
  - ports
id: 1560
categories:
  - Software
date: 2013-03-26 10:44:32
---

My most recent `# portmaster -Da` revealed a package conflict: py-setuptools was merged with py-distribute.

From FreshPorts:

{% blockquote %}

> 2013-03-05>
>
> Affects: users of devel/py-setuptools (i.e you)>
>
> Author: rm@FreeBSD.org>
>
> Reason: >
>   devel/py-setuptools was replaced with devel/py-distribute. py-setuptools port will be removed shortly.
{% endblockquote %}

To fix this:
`# portmaster -o devel/py-distribute devel/py-setuptools`

From `man 8 portmaster`:
{% blockquote %}
> -o &lt;new port dir in /usr/ports&gt; &lt;installed port&gt; >
>            replace the installed port with a port from a different origin
{% endblockquote %}
